{
  "texts": [
    "6E samples of HPCs associated with lower risk.",
    "Additional examples of tiles associated with HPCs are shown in Supplementary Fig. 9, where we can also see the coherence between the TCGA dataset and the NYU 1 external cohort.",
    "We then conducted a recurrence-free survival study on systemic and loco-regional recurrence in LUAD.",
    "In this case, we used NYU 1 as it provides detailed information of these types of recurrence and has considerably longer follow up times compared to the TCGA dataset, allowing a more refined study of recurrence.",
    "Once again we used a 5-fold cross-validation, achieving a mean c-index of 0.74 with 95% CI of 0.70-0.80 on NYU 1 (Fig. 6A, B)."
  ]
}